      "content": "interesting. so you're saying it's a pretty straightforward cause and effect then? i feel like a lot of economists argue there are other things going on too, like automation or just people getting older, but your point about the disincentive seems to be the main driver in what you're saying. why do you think that outweighs those other factors?",
